LibMMAPI -   Application programming interface for MMxD device
--------------------------------------------------------------

1. About software
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  It is an API library for MMxD Raspberry Pi based growing house controlling
  and remote monitoring device. You can write own handler application with
  this library easily. See manual page for available functions and procedures.

2. How to get installer package for my OS?
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
a. Visit homepage (see later) to download installer packages:

  FreeBSD:     libmmapi-0.1.txz
               libmmapi-0.1-FreeBSD-Port.shar  port package

  Linux:       libmmapi_0.1-1_i386.deb         Debian GNU/Linux
               libmmapi-0.1-i586-1.txz         Slackware
               libmmapi-0.1-1.i386.rpm         Suse Linux
               libmmapi-0.1-i586.bin           (linux-i586)
               libmmapi-0.1-i586.tar.gz        (linux-i586)

  Windows:     libmmapi-0.1-win32.exe
               libmmapi-0.1-win32.zip

  source:      libmmapi-0.1.tar.gz

b. Download from Github

  $ git clone https://github.com/pozsarzs/libmmapi.git

c. Download from Debian repository

  set reporitory:
  # echo "deb http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/ ./" >> /etc/apt/sources.list
  # wget -q -O - http://www.szerafingomba.hu/deb/KEY.gpg | apt-key add -
  # apt-get update

  install
  # apt-get install libmmapi

